    0   Ok.
    5   Error parsing args.

UMRES:
    Nothing.

@EndNode

@Node AR_SETTYPE "UrlManager.guide/ARexx/SetType"

@{b}SetType ID/A/N,TYPE/A@{ub}

Change the @{"type" Link TYPES} of an url.

Arguments:@{lindent 8}@{pari -4}
@{par}ID/A/N:
@{"ID" Link ID} of the url.
@{par}TYPE/A:
New @{"type" Link TYPES} of the url.
@{pard}@{lindent 0}

RC:
    0   Ok.
    1   ID not in use.
    5   Error parsing args.

UMRES:
    Nothing.

@EndNode

@Node AR_SETURL "UrlManager.guide/ARexx/SetUrl"

@{b}SetDepth ID/A/N,URL/A@{ub}

Change the name of an url.

Arguments:@{lindent 8}@{pari -4}
@{par}ID/A/N:
@{"ID" Link ID} of the url.
@{par}URL/A:
New name of the url.
@{pard}@{lindent 0}

RC:
    0   Ok.
    1   ID not in use.
    5   Error parsing args.

UMRES:
    Nothing.

@EndNode

